-- Phase 2 full seed — additive to Phase 1 (does NOT wipe existing rows).
-- Scales the catalog to ~20 specs across 5 valve families with:
--   * varied SPEC_REVISION history
--   * 1 base + 0-3 hyphen-suffix variants per spec
--   * CR history on selected structures (search needs real "Rev N" motion)
--   * 2 sub-assemblies referenced by parent structures' BOMs
--   * 1 archived, 1 locked, 1 below-target structure
--   * a peer engineer's DRAFT_STRUCTURE checked out
--   * 5 ASSIGNMENTs across 2 OM users (3 Open + 2 Acknowledged)
--   * cost PRICE_POINTs with quote_numbers + a handful of superseded rows
--   * structure_sell PRICE_POINTs per non-sub-assembly structure, sell-2026
--
-- New UUID ranges:
--   SPECs       30000000-...-00000000000{04..15}    (12 new + 3 from P1 = 15 specs)
--   Sub-asm SPEC 30000000-...-000000000099           (the catalog spec for sub-asms)
--   SPEC_REVs   31000000-...-{spec_id}NN
--   STRUCTUREs  40000000-...-{spec_id}NN            (NN = 01 base, 02-04 variants)
--   CRs / PRs   41/42000000-... matching structures
--   LINE_ITEMs  43000000-...-{struct_id}NN
--   PPs         50000000-...-0027 onward (component_cost)
--                          -1NN per structure_sell (continues from Phase 1)
--                          -8NN per subassembly_cost
--   ASSIGNMENTs 60000000-...
--   DRAFTs      reuse the STRUCTURE.id of the checked-out structure

